reviewText: Veeery funny man that I remember from years gone by on the Smother Brothers Show, Johnny Carson's Tonight Show. Is a very funny man that can really play the gituar. Takes me back 30-40 years, and he is still timeless and quick to quip. Loved it!
Enjoy watching video time after time.  Stafford is a great entertainer and we always enjoy watching his performances.  Would purchase again.
